snippet.title: Basketball Classics - Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Basketball Classics by Namo Gamo.
A new 5 on 5 arcade experience.  Now in full release on Steam.  

Developer Website:  http://namogamo.com/
Steam Store:  http://store.steampowered.com/app/819630/Basketball_Classics/

Trailer music by Aaron "Dya" Hickman
http://dyamusic.bandcamp.com/
